Usage: setMaxTranPerFreq [-help] [-force] -freq {freq1 freq2 ...}
                         [-lib <libName>] -pins {cell pin}
                         -tran {tran1 tran2 ...}

-help                             # Prints out the command usage
-force                            # Compute maxTran from interpolated -freq and
                                  # -tran values (bool, optional)
-freq {freq1 freq2 ...}           # specify a list of at least two frequency
                                  # values (list, required)
-lib <libName>                    # specify library name (string, optional)
-pins {cell pin}                  # Add new transition constraints to the
                                  # specified set of cells and pins
                                  # (list, required)
-tran {tran1 tran2 ...}           # specify a list of Nfreq transition values
                                  # (list, required)